Spectator Navigation With No Previous Visitation

Tag: 
Usability.Game.NavigationTime

Ambition:
Easy navigation to view functionalities of the game.

Meter: 
Stopwatch testing performed on 30 samples of random people.

Goal:
No more than 1 minute for 95 percent of games.

Scale: 
First time spectator with no account time to spectate a game that is in progress.

Meter: 
Average of last 30 samples.

Wish:
Less than 30 seconds for all samples.

Target: 
Less that 1 minute 90 percent of the time.